author: Home Repair Tutor
description: Entryway self leveling tips…I use sill seal against the stairs and wall. This gives me the necessary 1/8 inch expansion joint. I also seal the sill seal to the subfloor with silicone. Then I prime the floor, let that cure, and pour the self leveler. For detailed tutorials visit homerepairtutor.com🔥#selfleveling #floorprep #homerenovation #homerepairtutor
